Things TODO when releasing a new version (mostly for fann developers)

* No compile warnings
	cd examples
	make compiletest

* Everything should compile and install ok
	./configure && make
	su
	make install
	exit
	cd examples
	make runtest

* No memory leaks must exist
	cd examples
	rundebug

